By Bus: You can reach the library with bus lines 37A, 37E, 37Y and 38B. Visitors using the bus must get off at Talimhane Caddesi Station. It is a 5-minute walk from the station to the Library.

By Metro: You can reach the library via the M1A and M1B metro. Visitors using these metro lines should exit at Bayrampaşa station and transfer to the T4 Topkapı-Mescid-i Selam tram line. You can reach the Library by getting off at the Rami stop of the T4 Topkapı-Mescid-i Selam tram line.


By Minibus: You can reach the Library with the minibus lines A-27 and A-74. Visitors using this route must get off the minibus at the Rami Kışla Caddesi or Talimhane Caddesi stops.


By Tram: You can reach the Library by getting off at the Rami stop on the T4 Topkapı-Mescid-i Selam tram line.


If you are driving to the Library, you can park your car in the private parking lot of the Rami Library, which can accommodate 144 cars. The Municipality of Eyüp also offers a paid parking lot with capacity for 500 vehicles.
